text: Yuri Farneti (born 3 January 1996 in Angera) is an Italian professional squash player.https://psaworldtour.com/players/view/6684/yuri-farneti As of February 2018, he was ranked number 170 in the world, and number 1 in Italy. He has played in the main draw of many professional PSA tournaments and competed in the World Games.https://www.oasport.it/2017/06/squash-yuri-farneti-ai-world- games-2017-sorteggiati-i-tabelloni/ As of February 2018, he was the highest ranked Italian player. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male squash players Category:Competitors at the 2017 World Games
title: Yuri Farneti
